==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Chloral
<hw>Chlo"ral</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Chlor</ets>ine
+ <ets>al</ets>cohol.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A
colorless oily liquid, <chform>CCl3.CHO</chform>, of a pungent odor and
harsh taste, obtained by the action of chlorine upon ordinary or ethyl
alcohol.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Chloral hydrate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chloralamide</ent>⟦br⟧
